{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151788, "create_time": 1653563095, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "草！", "timestamp": 1653563095}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151795, "create_time": 1653563269, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "什么智障", "timestamp": 1653563269}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151813, "create_time": 1653563626, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "处罚的原因不在于接触猫会传播疫情，而在于万一被咬伤后在医疗资源紧张的情况下难以调集到狂犬病疫苗", "timestamp": 1653563626}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151818, "create_time": 1653563689, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "我看到的说法是这个时间点如果被抓伤了，学校去搞狂犬病疫苗也不一定搞得来（）", "timestamp": 1653563689}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151858, "create_time": 1653564421, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "什么智障", "timestamp": 1653564421}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151859, "create_time": 1653564424, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "就事论事，因为逗猫就给这种处罚很不合理。", "timestamp": 1653564424}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151874, "create_time": 1653564702, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "“没办法了，闵行区中心医院的犬伤科现在只有一组人员，如果到交大来打疫苗，这段时间就必须停诊，所以同学只能出校去打狂犬疫苗了。”", "timestamp": 1653564702}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151877, "create_time": 1653564760, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "去到校外注射，将会面临许多问题：\n在校外疫情防控形势较为紧张的情况下，校内人员出校后短时间内无法进校，外出打疫苗就会存在几个问题：\n1）如何前往医院（现在交通工具上路必须有通行证）\n2）疫苗需要三针闭环，外出就医后需要自行寻找宾馆入住，并且隔离。\n3）何时能返校仍是未知\n4）食物供应困难", "timestamp": 1653564760}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151880, "create_time": 1653564821, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Bob: 这是四月份出现类似事件后的通报", "timestamp": 1653564821}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151892, "create_time": 1653565118, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "？？", "timestamp": 1653565118}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151900, "create_time": 1653565229, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 现在都能靠臆想来定罪了吗", "timestamp": 1653565229}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151915, "create_time": 1653565415, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Dave: 这不是臆想啊？之前是专门发布了这个规定的。起初三四月份出现这种情况的时候是口头批评教育，不过类似情况依旧时有发生，所以后来就改成了通报批评", "timestamp": 1653565415}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151924, "create_time": 1653565470, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "所以身在疫情区域连和小动物接触的权利都没有了", "timestamp": 1653565470}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151926, "create_time": 1653565497, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Dave: 这是现实啊，四月份有人被抓了自己打不到疫苗，最后是学校到处装孙子", "timestamp": 1653565497}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151943, "create_time": 1653565800, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Francis: 问题是你被咬伤之后怎么办呢？谁来负这个责任呢？有人说后果个人自负，但是如果真被咬伤了学校不可能坐视不管呀？", "timestamp": 1653565800}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 151967, "create_time": 1653566235, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "理智看待，校方其实做了很多努力，只是还有人作", "timestamp": 1653566235}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 152010, "create_time": 1653566771, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Bob: 医疗资源不足怪学生是吧😅", "timestamp": 1653566771}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 152026, "create_time": 1653567025, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Isabella: 那你说咋办？现在让你当交大校长，你说该咋管理？", "timestamp": 1653567025}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 152073, "create_time": 1653567655, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "学生把自己当孩子，学校就会让自己做家长", "timestamp": 1653567655}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 152093, "create_time": 1653567961, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Bob: 经典你行你上，某些小鬼不去想想医疗资源不足的根源在哪，反倒是共情起学校一起自我反思来了", "timestamp": 1653567961}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 152134, "create_time": 1653568493, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Isabella: 你现在说的轻巧，谁不知道医疗资源不足的根源在哪？可当你坐在交大校长这个位子上，甚至坐到上海市委书记这个位子上的时候，你真的敢拿出勇气说出来吗？", "timestamp": 1653568493}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153464, "create_time": 1653582194, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Jason: 听家长话的才是孩子，成年人都知道和小动物互动是个人自由，没有损害别人利益", "timestamp": 1653582194}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153541, "create_time": 1653583059, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 另一个洞里有人发了这篇从3月份起类似事件的发展历程https://www.zhihu.com/question/534655842/answer/2502670084", "timestamp": 1653583059}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153589, "create_time": 1653583684, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 因为你在北京，你不在上海，你以为被猫抓了就去看医生是一件很简单的事情，你没有亲历过有两个需要抢救的病人但是只有一辆救护车的困境。在这种情况下，学校无力改变医疗资源短缺的情况，只能希望尽量避免这样的困境发生，不去因为这样的事而去挤占宝贵的资源，把有限的救护资源尽量留给更需要的人。当然这种情况正在好转，相信随着城市逐渐恢复平常，一些特殊的政策也将会不断放开。", "timestamp": 1653583684}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153596, "create_time": 1653583797, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "我寻思这事早就发过通告，有些人手贱怎么还能得到维护呢", "timestamp": 1653583797}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 153671, "create_time": 1653584947, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "Re Eve: 只要被抓了保证自己有办法打疫苗，找不到办法打疫苗真得病要死的时候不找麻烦，谁关心你摸不摸猫", "timestamp": 1653584947}], "create_time": 1653563084, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653568493, "likenum": 12, "n_attentions": 12, "n_comments": 21, "pid": 50993, "poll": null, "reply": 21, "text": "匪常智障\n![](https://bafkreigdot77ekpz4ut4wowngczje5y4foktdfewu7rlcf4quvbv6xqv7u.ipfs.hub.textile.io/?filename=%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20220526205526.jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreigdot77ekpz4ut4wowngczje5y4foktdfewu7rlcf4quvbv6xqv7u)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1653563084}}